# Data Class script: CCMCHGREQ_CSTD, Change Request - Header
# Issue 109096/2 - 2015-11-20 by BAKHA : send e-mail notifications to QA manager, planner,
#                                        creater, and approvers
# Issue 109094/15 - 2015-11-30 by BAKHA : allow multiple non-conformances for same product at any status
